Ok, just found this vid/post today, hoping beyond hope that no one saw my most ignorant post about it earlier. 

 Anyway, yeah, that&#39;s random, but I don&#39;t see how it can be used to sweep a radio in it&#39;s present form. Have a feeling some information with held. It almost implies Hultay made the random sweep work, which I know is highly unlikely. 

 Anyway, trying a new idea picked off the vid. 

 BTW, has the question ever occured to anyone--why random sweep? Answer; cuz the first box was made after I used EVPmaker, which chops up the audio and plays it back--randomly. That&#39;s why I thought the sweep had to be random. Yeah, the first 20 some boxes were random only, and did work, contrary to what you&#39;ve been told by one scumbag.

 My aplogoies, but guys like Hultay really piss me off, and it takes a few days to screw my head back on. Yeah, and people claiming to be psychic mediums don&#39;t see through the lies.

 Oh well, ain&#39;t gonna matter.

F-S 

